(1, 1, '2015-03-22 23:57:09', '2015-03-22 23:57:09', '<a href="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Libra-Full-Moon-4.png"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-56 alignleft" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Libra-Full-Moon-4-300x251.png" alt="Libra Full Moon (4)" width="300" height="251" /></a>Its full moon time mama''s and this one''s a biggy because its an eclipse and is super charges and super powerful. It falls in the sign of Libra today, meaning the theme around this full moon is alla bout balance. Im feeling it as the balance bewtween my ''me time'' against my ''baby time''. If youre feeling stressed, snappy and out of wack then youre probably out of balance..and we all know what side we''re giving all our energy too - let me say its surely not the ''im going to have another cocktail by the pool followed by a massage side!''\r\nSo, for the next 2 weeks (until the new moon that is) im going to TRY schedual in some me time and bring things back into balance..Any ideas on some quick me time fixes mama''s?..mani pedi anyone?', 'Libra Full Moon Total Eclipse', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2015-07-14 12:07:12', '2015-07-14 12:07:12', '', 0, 'https://www.spiritmama.com.au/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
