ve faith that this is where you are meant to be right here, right now.\r\n\r\nMiraculously this all worked for me. With my energy lighter and calmer, I got a rock star car park, shopping was a breeze and Indi was a dream, all done and dusted. Amazing what changing up your energy can do for the rest of your day.\r\n\r\nSo tell me mama, how have you snapped out of stress quickly with the kids?<img class=" size-full wp-image-68 alignleft" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/signature.png" alt="signature" width="171" height="53" />', '4 Ways to Snap out of Stress', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-21 04:19:13', '2015-07-21 04:19:13', '', 78, 'http://www.spiritmama.com.au/?p=83', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
