(84, 1, '2015-05-21 04:27:33', '2015-05-21 04:27:33', 'Why do we as mums feel like we should be ‘doing’ more?\r\n\r\nI find myself feeling like I should be doing more with myself, more with my time, more with my life.<a href="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2.png"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-85 alignleft" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2-300x251.png" alt="2" width="300" height="251" /></a> In reality I am already so full. Not only do I have a 3yr old and a baby who is 1 but I find myself as I’m changing a nappy thinking of big ideas and dreams I would like to accomplish, who I would like to be. What I would like to do..but why isn''t what I’m doing already, enough?\r\n\r\nBeing a mum is hard work. Full stop. Period. There are no days off; it’s the toughest, most rewarding job in the world. So why do we feel like we should be doing more?\r\n\r\nBeing a mother encompasses so many roles. We sing, we dance, and we perform circus tricks. We are highly efficient in the art of multitasking and negotiation. We’re a chef, doctor and chauffer all rolled into one and to top it off we wipe bums all day!\r\n\r\nRemember back in the day when being anything other than a good house wife and mother was pretty much unheard of. Jobs and career were for the men. Maybe it’s a generation thing..But I want to be an amazing mother, fabulous wife and a successful, creative entrepreneur!\r\n\r\nBut you know what? The more I try to ''do'' it all, the more resistance starts to build, there''s no ''me time'' in those luscious life roles, so stress inevitably sets in <u>unless</u> I have balance.\r\n\r\nYou see, I believe we can have it all, as long as we make time for ourselves first.\r\n\r\nSo my practice for today is to stop trying to do it all. To stop looking for fulfilment in all these external labels and just be.\r\n\r\nBe who I am in this moment....which is mum x\r\n\r\n<img class=" size-full wp-image-68 alignleft" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/signature.png" alt="signature" width="171" height="53" />', 'Isn''t being mum enough?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'isnt-being-mum-enough', '', '', '2015-07-22 04:12:25', '2015-07-22 04:12:25', '', 0, 'http://www.spiritmama.com.au/?p=84', 0, 'post', '', 0),
