s a greater force at work here and for some reason you’re stuck or held up. Have faith that this is where you are meant to be right here, right now.\r\n\r\nMiraculously this all worked for me. With my energy lighter and calmer, I got a rock star car park, shopping was a breeze and Indi was a dream, all done and dusted. Amazing what changing up your energy can do for the rest of your day.\r\n\r\nSo tell me mama, how have you snapped out of stress quickly with the kids?\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/signature.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-68" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/signature.png" alt="signature" width="171" height="53" /></a>', '4 Ways to Snap out of Stress', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-22 00:09:58', '2015-07-22 00:09:58', '', 78, 'http://www.spiritmama.com.au/?p=93', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2015-03-26 04:18:14', '2015-03-26 04:18:14', '<a href="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/These-Simple-Words-Changed-Everything.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-97" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/These-Simple-Words-Changed-Everything.png" alt="These Simple Words Changed Everything" width="940" height="788" /></a>Amongst the hustle and bustle of the mornings business, the half-eaten toast and pyjamas flung around the house. As I try to get 2 kids plus myself ready for the day (it should be an Olympic sport) and with all the rush rush rushing and ‘come oooonnnns!!!” I stopped myself this morning mid-stream and got down to eye level with Ollie. I looked into those bottomless pools of green blue, his own little cosmos and said\r\n\r\n“Ollie, I would just like to say thank you honey”\r\n\r\nHe said ‘That’s ok Mummy” not really knowing what I was thanking him for J\r\n\r\nI continued to say “Thank you for being born baby, thank you for choosing me as your mummy. You make me so happy”\r\n\r\nHe said “really?” I felt his recognition of what I had said sink in.\r\n\r\n“I am so lucky that every day I get to wake up to you, play with you, kiss and cuddle you *insert kiss and cuddle here * You are so important to me. I love you.”\r\n\r\nSometimes we get so busy being mum that we forget to tell the ones we love how special they are. This small act of stopping and connecting, of speaking from my heart made my day…and I’m sure made his too.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-68" src="http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/signature.png" alt="signature" width="171" height="53" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'These Simple Words Changed Everything', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '94', '', '', '2015-07-22 04:21:45', '2015-07-22 04:21:45', '', 0, 'http://www.spiritmama.com.au/?p=94', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(95, 1, '2015-07-22 04:14:33', '2015-07-22 04:14:33', '', 'Ollie', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'ollie', '', '', '2015-07-22 04:14:33', '2015-07-22 04:14:33', '', 94, 'http://www.spiritmama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Ollie.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
